      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, reliable condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior is clean with only minor surface scratches and small stone chips consistent with regular use, while the interior remains comfortable and free of major tears or stains. Mechanically, the car runs smoothly, though it may soon require standard maintenance items like new brake pads or tires. It is a solid, dependable choice for anyone looking for a quality pre-owned vehicle that has many miles left to give.",
