    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, presenting as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior features a flawless paint finish with a deep, mirror-like shine, free of any scratches, chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is immaculate, with premium materials that show no signs of wear and all electronic features functioning perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in peak performance, having been meticulously maintained with a complete service history and no pending needs. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that drives as beautifully as it looks.",
