    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Calling all project seekers and restoration fans! This vehicle is ready for a second act and is looking for an owner with the skills to bring it back to its former glory. While it's currently in poor condition and needs significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it's a fantastic foundation for anyone who loves a rewarding challenge and a great deal!",
