      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Experience the perfect synergy of sophistication and reliability. This vehicle has been exceptionally well-maintained, passing our comprehensive safety and performance evaluation with ease. Featuring a refined interior and a robust powertrain, it offers a level of comfort and dependability that is rare to find in this segment. This is a premier opportunity to acquire a high-caliber vehicle that delivers consistent excellence on every journey.",
      "price": 38500.0,
